(against whom they had rebelled) and <HI>Amraphel,</HI>
and the other Kings which had conquered them,
and sackt the place; they did not think of a more
<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">urious enemy, who was arming himself against
them, even the King of Heaven, against whom
