<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">rank, they did not think that their flesh, and all
<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">he provisions thereof should so soon be devoured
by flames; they bought, and they sold, they did little
