<LIST>
<ITEM>1. Flee from Sin.</ITEM>
<ITEM>2. Flee unto Christ,</ITEM>
</LIST>
<P>If you would <HI>flee</HI> from <HI>wrath</HI> and <HI>Hell.</HI></P>
<LIST>
<ITEM>Or, 1. <HI>Repent of Sin.</HI></ITEM>
<ITEM>2. Get an interest in Christ.</ITEM>
</LIST>
<P>And then you may be able to stand with confi|dence
